 2010-13432010-10-28,  ,  ,  ,  FIN,  HRSD
ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectYear 2011 Premium Rate limit change
PrecisOrder changing the maximum percentage by which the Employment Insurance (EI) PREMIUM RATE may be increased or decreased each year to no more than five one-hundredths of one per cent in 2011 and to no more than ten one-hundredths of one per cent in 2012 and thereafter.
